urdu transliteration text:
Jo tujhay khof hain shayad main usay kam kardoonAaja aankhon pai teray naad-e-ali dam kardoonDoor kyun baiti hai aa meri Sakina soja
Let me recite Nad-e-Ali for you,
@HujjatELC

Iss tarah soyi Takallum woh yateema bibiMaa uthaati rahi, uthi na Sakina bibiPhir na Bano ne kaha, meri Sakina so ja
Her mother kept trying, but Sakina never woke up,
@HujjatELC
